@0 = ~Enemy forces penetrated the palace...I tried to reach you and Imoen before they did, but... well.~
@1 = ~So, <CHARNAME>. The <PRO_MANWOMAN>. The myth. The hero of the Sword Coast. We've accomplished much together, haven't we.~
@2 = ~I'm glad we'll be working together again, <CHARNAME>.~
@3 = ~You did what you could, and I thank you for it. Is everyone else safe?~
@4 = ~Not that I know of.~ 
@5 = ~That we have, Corwin. (You sip your drink) It looks as though our work isn't finished, however. Tell me what you know of Caelar and her crusade.~ 